components.name: PricingSection
components.code:
const auth = useAuth();

  const plans = [
    {
      id: "starter",
      name: "Business Starter",
      price: "950",
      perks: [
        "Business Strategy",
        "Strategy Execution plan ",
        "Go-to-market strategy ",
         "Access to curated articles and short videos only for members ",
      ],
    },
    {
      id: "pro",
      name: "Business Growth ",
      price: "2000",
      perks: [
        "Brand Audit. Deep Evaluation of your current business position ",
        "Strategy development and implementation support",
        "Take a look at your financial model and offer financial advice and insight",
        "Deep dive into your pricing strategy and its implementation",
        "Developing a Consistent Revenue Stream that increases profitability",
        "Developing a Consistent Brand Presence",
         "Organizational development",
      ],
    },
    {
      id: "business",
      name: "Marketing Focus",
      price: "1200",
      perks: [
        "Marketing strategy development",
        "Branding",
        "Market research",
        "Search engine optimization (SEO)",
        "Social Media Strategy",
        "Implementation",
        "Monitoring",
      ],
    },
  ];

children.attributes:
{
  component: "a",
  variant: "contained",
  color: "primary",
  size: "large",
  fullWidth: true,
  href: auth.user
    ? `/purchase/${plan.id}`
    : `/auth/signup?next=/purchase/${plan.id}`,
}
